OL,3,C'I feel like a human now' - Nelson
OL,4,Cgains citizenship after 48 years in
OL,5,Cthe UK
OL,7,FVictoria Grimes has been speaking to
OL,8,FNelson at his home in Wirral.
OL,10,FA man described as a 'local legend' on
OL,11,FMerseyside says he's 'overwhelmed'
OL,12,Fafter finally being granted full
OL,13,FBritish citizenship, 48 years after
OL,14,Fmoving to the country.
OL,16,FNelson Shardey has lived in the
OL,17,Fcountry since arriving as a student
OL,18,Ffrom Ghana in 1977, but in 2019 he was
OL,19,Ftold he had no right to live in the UK.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
