PN,39702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1772478695
OL,3,C'I feel like a human now' - Nelson
OL,4,Cgains citizenship after 48 years in
OL,5,Cthe UK
OL,7,FThe retired shopkeeper, who ran
OL,8,FNelson's News in Wallasey for 31
OL,9,Fyears, was told he was not British
OL,10,Fwhen. he applied for a passport to
OL,11,Freturn to Ghana for his mother's
OL,12,Ffuneral in 2019.
OL,14,F"When I got hold of my certificate I
OL,15,Fwas overwhelmed," the 76-year old told
OL,16,FITV Granada Reports.
OL,18,F"I said, thank God. I felt like
OL,19,Fpunching the air."
OL,26,@vD@AOUwD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
