CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1772478695
OL,3,C'I feel like a human now' - Nelson
OL,4,Cgains citizenship after 48 years in
OL,5,Cthe UK
OL,7,FMr Shardey has performed jury service
OL,8,Fand was given a police bravery award
OL,9,Ffor tackling a robber who was
OL,10,Fattacking someone with a baseball bat.
OL,12,FHowever, the Home Office previously
OL,13,Ftold him that he would need to apply
OL,14,Ffor the 10-year route to settlement,
OL,15,Fwhich would cost around #7,000.
OL,17,FNelson also faced paying more than
OL,18,F#10,000 to access the NHS so he could
OL,19,Fhave regular cancer check-ups.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
