PN,39704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1772478695
OL,3,C'I feel like a human now' - Nelson
OL,4,Cgains citizenship after 48 years in
OL,5,Cthe UK
OL,7,FHe recalled, "I said, what is wrong?
OL,8,FI'm working. I pay my tax. I don't
OL,9,Fbreak the law. I help a lot of people
OL,10,Fwho are in difficulty."
OL,12,FMr Shardey was given indefinite leave
OL,13,Fto remain in 2024 after his family
OL,14,Flaunched a campaign to have his case
OL,15,Freviewed.
OL,17,FNelson's son, Aaron, said, "It's been
OL,18,Fsuch a journey to get here. It's been
OL,19,Ftesting.
OL,26,@oD@NOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
