OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1772478695
OL,3,C'I feel like a human now' - Nelson
OL,4,Cgains citizenship after 48 years in
OL,5,Cthe UK
OL,7,F"It just shows the power of community
OL,8,Fand how everyone around us came
OL,9,Ftogether to support us."
OL,11,FNelson is now looking forward to
OL,12,Fgetting a passport and finally being
OL,13,Fable to travel.
OL,15,FThe remaining money from his
OL,16,Ffundraising campaign has been donated
OL,17,Fto charity.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
