PN,39706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1772478695
OL,3,C'I feel like a human now' - Nelson
OL,4,Cgains citizenship after 48 years in
OL,5,Cthe UK
OL,7,FHe added, "I feel really, really
OL,8,Fhappy. I feel like I'm a human being.
OL,9,FI feel relieved and part of where I
OL,10,Fam, the community."
OL,12,F"When someone tells you you are not
OL,13,Fwho you think you are, you have to
OL,14,Ffight for it."
OL,26,@oD@KOUtD@AOU
